<font color="#FF0000">THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Wed Nov 27  4:33:37 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
I went to DC with the intention of paying respects to those I left behind and perhaps finding some sort of closure for myself. At the base of the Washington Monument I looked at the Wall like I looked at the treeline and relived the fear knowing I could not approach it yet.
